title: Two Sides to Every Date: The Unsanitary Beard
description: Kevin emailed us wanting to find out why Tara ghosted him.  Kevin couldn't be on-air with us but we get Tara on the phone and she tells us something that she realized she's just not into, so therefore she didn't want to continue to date Kevin.
